            <note xml:id="foot.f3">The reference is to <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_2367.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">William Jackson Hooker</ref>. See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-4807.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from J. D. Hooker, [7–8 April 1865]</ref>.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f4">This nephew has not been identified.</note>
